snippet.textDisplay:
Excellent and heart touching song. India-Pakistan relations can be extremely good and cordial,  provided they resolve Kashmir and make it as a sovereign buffer state. This would end hatred and allow for people to people contact between the two nations. 

To add, India and Pakistan were never one. They were created by British. Only Punjab and Sindh got divided and JK lost its independence in the process. Rest, nothing was common, as generally taught to students in India.
